{"word":"Elah","slug":"elah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Elah</b> <a href=\"#/H414\">H414</a><br/><a href=\"#/H425\">H425</a> <br/> 1. A valley where David slew Goliath<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=2'>1Sa 17:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=19'>1Sa 17:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=21&verse=9'>1Sa 21:9</a><br/> 2. An Edomitish duke<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=41'>Gen 36:41</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=52'>1Ch 1:52</a><br/> 3. Son of Caleb<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=15'>1Ch 4:15</a><br/> 4. Father of Shimei<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=18'>1Ki 4:18</a><br/> 5. Son and successor of Baasha, king of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=14'>1Ki 16:14</a><br/> 6. Father of Hoshea<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=15&verse=30'>2Ki 15:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=17&verse=1'>2Ki 17:1</a><br/> 7. A Benjamite chief<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=8'>1Ch 9:8</a>"}]}